      "type": "concept",
      "title": "Details",
      "content": "\u00ab\n1\n2\n3\n4\n5\n6\n\u00bb\nBasic Pagination\nIf you have a web site with many pages, you may want to use some sort of pagination.\nTo create a basic pagination, use buttons (\nw3-button\n) in a \nbar (\nw3-bar\n).\nExample\n<div class=\"w3-bar\">\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">1</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">2</a>\n<a href=\"#\" \n  class=\"w3-button\">3</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">4</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">5</a>\n</div>\n\nTo remove the space between the buttons add a\nw3-bar-item\nclass:\nExample\n<div class=\"w3-bar\">\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">&laquo;</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">1</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">2</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">3</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">4</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">5</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">&raquo;</a>\n</div>\n\nPagination Arrows\nUse HTML entities or icons from an icon library to add pagination arrows:\n\u00ab\n1\n2\n3\n4\n\u00bb\nExample\n<div class=\"w3-bar\">\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">&laquo;</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">1</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">2</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">3</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">4</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">5</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">&raquo;</a>\n</div>\n\nActive/Current Link\n\u00ab\n1\n2\n3\n4\n\u00bb\nUse one of the\nw3-\ncolor\nclasses to indicate which page the user is on:\nExample\n<div class=\"w3-bar\">\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">&laquo;</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button w3-green\">1</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">2</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">3</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">4</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">&raquo;</a>\n</div>\n\nHover Color\n\u00ab\n1\n2\n3\n4\n\u00bb\nBy default, when you move the mouse over the pagination links, they get a grey background color. Use any of the\nw3-hover-\ncolor\nclasses to change the hover color:\nExample\n<div class=\"w3-bar\">\n<a href=\"#\" \nclass=\"w3-button w3-hover-purple\">&laquo;</a>\n<a \n  href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button w3-hover-green\">1</a>\n<a href=\"#\" \n  class=\"w3-button w3-hover-red\">2</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button \n  w3-hover-blue\">3</a>\n<a href=\"#\" \nclass=\"w3-button w3-hover-black\">4</a>\n<a href=\"#\" \nclass=\"w3-button w3-hover-orange\">&raquo;</a>\n</div>\n\nPagination Sizing\n\u00ab\n1\n2\n3\n4\n\u00bb\n\u00ab\n1\n2\n3\n4\n\u00bb\nUse\nw3-tiny\n,\nw3-small\n,\nw3-large\n,\nw3-xlarge\n,\nw3-xxlarge\nor\nw3-xxxlarge\nto size the pagination:\nExample\n<div class=\"w3-bar \nw3-xlarge\">\n\nCentered Pagination\n\u00ab\n1\n2\n3\n4\n\u00bb\nTo center the pagination, put the \"w3-bar\" element inside a \"w3-center\" element:\nExample\n<div class=\"w3-center\">\n<div class=\"w3-bar\">\n<a href=\"#\" \n  class=\"w3-bar-item w3-button\">&laquo;</a>\n<a href=\"#\" \n  class=\"w3-button\">1</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">2</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">3</a>\n<a href=\"#\" \n  class=\"w3-button\">4</a>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button\">&raquo;</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\nBordered Pagination\n\u00ab\n1\n2\n3\n4\n5\n\u00bb\nAdd the\nw3-border\nclass to create a pagination with borders:\nExample\n<div class=\"w3-bar \nw3-border\">\n\nRounded Borders\n\u00ab\n1\n2\n3\n4\n5\n\u00bb\nAdd the\nw3-round\nclass \nExample\n<div class=\"w3-bar \nw3-border w3-round\">\n\nOther Pagination Examples\nThe w3-bar class can also be used to create\n\n\u276f\n\n<div class=\"w3-bar w3-border w3-round\">\n<a href=\"#\" \n  class=\"w3-button\">&#10094; \n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-button \n  w3-right\">\n</div>\n\nHome\nLink 1\nLink 2\nLink 3\nInline Menu Example\n<div class=\"w3-show-inline-block\">\n<div class=\"w3-bar w3-light-grey\">\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"w3-bar-item w3-button w3-dark-grey\">Home</a>\n<a \n  href=\"#\" class=\"w3-bar-item w3-button\">Link 1</a>\n<a href=\"#\" \n  class=\"w3-bar-item w3-button\">Link 2</a>\n<a href=\"#\" \n  class=\"w3-bar-item w3-button\">Link 3</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\u2605\n+1",
